---
title: Rustic Lamb Spaghetti Bolognese with Parmesan Cheese
description: Comfort food, but make it quick! This bolognese brings rich, slow-cooked flavour in a fraction of the time. Perfectly al dente spaghetti gets tossed with a hearty lamb and tomato ragu and topped with a generous sprinkle of Parmesan cheese. It’s a cosy, satisfying classic, made easy!
